23 website to reflect the changes pursuant to [section 1].
24
25 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Effective dates. (1) Except as provided in subsection (2), [this act] is
26 effective on passage and approval.
27 (2) [Section 3 4] is effective July 1, 2025.
